text.data-name: The ‘Coral & Marina’ Hotel is one of the main hotels in Ensenad

g.text: The ‘Coral & Marina’ Hotel is one of the main hotels in Ensenada,big part of the tourism that arrives in the city decides to stay here,but currently there has been a growth in the hotel business.Therefore, as a company it has been decided to develop and implement an application to give visibility to the hotel, in the same way it was decided to create a dashboard is required to easily manage the mobile application. The application developed for this company offers a clean and clear management for hotel staff. The hotel now has the ability to manually record who will be staff in charge of the position to control the application and likewise monitor, edit and preview the content that will be given to users.
